title: The Walking Dead: Season Two v1.0 (EP 1-3) Android
description:
In the game The Walking Dead: Season 2 continues the story of Clementine, a girl orphaned by the invasion of the undead. Forced to take care of herself, she learns to survive in a crazy world. Many months have passed since the events of The Walking Dead: Season 1, and Clementine is trying to secure safety. But as a normal child can survive when the living is no better and sometimes worse than dead? Playing as Clementines, you will encounter situations and dilemmas, test your moral qualities and the survival instinct. In this sequel to one of the best games of 2012 your decisions and actions change history. Before installing,

To install the game requires ~ 2.0 GB of free space in the internal memory. Installation may take a long time, have patience.
